description: Updates the data stored on an Amazon Q in Connect Session.

parameters.name: assistantId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q in Connect assistant. Can be either the ID or the ARN. URLs cannot contain the ARN.

parameters.name: sessionId
parameters.description: The identifier of the session. Can be either the ID or the ARN. URLs cannot contain the ARN.

parameters.name: data
parameters.description: The data stored on the Amazon Q in Connect Session. (dict) --- The list of key-value pairs that are stored on the session. The key of the data stored on the session. The value of the data stored on the session. stringValue (string) --- The string value of the data stored on the session.

nested_params.name: key
nested_params.description: The key of the data stored on the session.

nested_params.name: value
nested_params.description: The value of the data stored on the session.

nested_params.name: stringValue
nested_params.description: The string value of the data stored on the session.

nested_items.name: sessionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the session.

nested_items.name: namespace
nested_items.description: The namespace into which the session data is stored. Supported namespaces are: Custom.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: The key of the data stored on the session.

nested_items.name: stringValue
nested_items.description: The string value of the data stored on the session.
